last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 1
last_episode_to_air.overview: The female Elite team head to Brussels to battle the best artistic gymnasts in Europe at the start of the season, but for Amelie, one of the UK's brightest young stars, things take a dramatic twist. And Nile Wilson, back from his incredible success at the Commonwealth Games, sets the first of his Gym Star Challenges.

name: Gym Stars
overview: In this series we go behind the scenes of the lives of some of the UK's most promising young gymnasts.
